data.description: Seller has sanded and re stained floors  upstairs bedrooms. New hot water in this week too! Welcome to this stunning 1952 sq. ft. home located in the desirable Hamilton  neighborhood of Baltimore City. This charming property boasts beautiful hardwood floors throughout, giving it a warm and inviting feel. Freshly painted walls create a crisp and clean ambiance, while the granite countertops add a touch of elegance to the kitchen space. The updated bathrooms offer modern fixtures and finishes, providing both style and convenience. Additionally, this home has undergone a beautiful renovation, showcasing its timeless appeal. Located in close proximity to sought-after charter schools, this property offers an excellent opportunity for families looking to provide their children with quality education.  Please inquiry about FHLB Grant Money up to $15K for down payment or closing help. Call listing agent for more info.    The current loan is an FHA assumable at 4% .Just another option on financing this property
